\f0\b \cf2 Episode 12 \'96 The Adaptable Mindset \
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 Wayne Gretzky, the greatest hockey player of all time, said this: "I skate to where the puck is going, not where it's been." \
